description:
This is a 26 minute workout called 'Full Body Yoga for Strength & Flexibility | 25 Minute At Home Mobility Routine' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
